---
title: Cheesy Creamy Chicken and Cauliflower Pasta with Baby Spinach
description: Making the perfect mac 'n’ cheese starts with a velvety cheddar cheese sauce and a swirl of cream. Hearty chicken, roasted cauliflower and a sprinkle of chili flakes add elegance to this everyday favourite!
